<p style="line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; text-indent: 0; margin: 0"><font color="maroon">What is an affiliate program?</font><a name="1"></a><br><BR>
An affiliate program allows you to sell products from your Web page or within your emails, without responsibility for inventory, shipping, credit card authorization, customer service or order tracking. You still get a percentage of the sales (which is pure profit), and all you have to do is present the products you want to sell on your site. By becoming a TravelVideoStore.com affiliate, you can link to any one of our over 5,000 Travel related titles, including videos in VHS and DVD! Every time a consumer places an order with us that was generated from your site, you get a percentage of that sale. We include all the instructions of how to set up links to our site, label yourself as a TravelVideoStore.com affiliate and even show product availability in real time. .</p>
