<p style="line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; text-indent: 0; margin: 0"><font color="maroon">How do I link from my site to yours?</font><a name="7"></a><br><br>
By using a specially formatted link, our site will track all the customers who click through your site to ours. This link contains your Affiliate ID and all the information that our site needs to track the user.  Once you are signed up as an Affiliate, you will have access to a detailed description of how to create these special links. You will also have access to an automated generator that can create these links for you.  You would then simply copy the code provided into the appropriate place within your website or HTML email.  We provide links to our home page, to individual categories such as "Italy", "Paris", "Grand Canyon National Park", "Carnival Cruise Lines" to name a few.  Also, we support links to individual products, this can be useful for email communications with your customers or direct placement on your website.</p>
